{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/development/2019-01-18-pwa2/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Code & Coffee","author":"Seunghun Kang","siteUrl":"https://bluelion2.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"bluelion2/bluelion2.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"bluelion2"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"909047e2-e1a4-5d56-a4a3-cab300574faa","excerpt":"Progressive Web App에 대해 공부합니다.\n장기효님의 PWA 시작하기 2. PWA에 필요한 것들 1. manifest.json 2. service-worker.js 참고자료 Google I.O 2018","html":"<p>Progressive Web App에 대해 공부합니다.\n<a href=\"https://www.inflearn.com/course/pwa/\">장기효님의 PWA 시작하기</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"2-pwa에-필요한-것들\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-pwa%EC%97%90-%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94%ED%95%9C-%EA%B2%83%EB%93%A4\" aria-label=\"2 pwa에 필요한 것들 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. PWA에 필요한 것들</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-manifestjson\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-manifestjson\" aria-label=\"1 manifestjson permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. manifest.json</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">-   PWA에 대한 설정을 할 수 있는 json 파일\n\n-   모바일 화면에 보여지기 위한 이름, 아이콘, 클릭시 들어오는 화면과 배경색 들을 지정할 수 있다.\n\n-   short_name, name, 아이콘은 필수로 있어야 함</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"2-service-workerjs\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-service-workerjs\" aria-label=\"2 service workerjs permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. service-worker.js</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">-   브라우저 내에 보여지지 않는 부분에서 움직이는 JS파일 - 자체 스코프를 가짐.\n\n-   브라우저와 서버 사이를 연결하는 브릿지 역할\n\n-   web과 mobile에서 push 알림을 설정 할 수 있음.\n\n-   페이지를 닫는다고 죽지 않음 - 브라우저를 닫아야 종료\n\n-   Dom에 직접 접근이 불가함.</code></pre></div>\n<p>참고자료</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NITk4kXMQDw&#x26;t=493s\">Google I.O 2018</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Progressive Web app 2","date":"January 18, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/development/2019-01-18-pwa2/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/essay/2019-01-11-주간회고/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"주간회고 1/4 ~ 1/11","category":"essay","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/development/2019-01-19-pwa3/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Progressive Web app 3","category":"development","draft":false}}}}}